# steps

1. Create word2vec from text
    > python3 clear_create_word2vec.py 

2. Convert word2vec file to ids matrix as an numpy file format in order to use with tensorflow
    > python3 numpy_embedding_matrix_tf.py

3. Use embedding matrix with tensorflow 
    In progress...

